description: [``botocore``] Doc-only update around removing AL1 from list of available AMIs for Cloud9

[``botocore``] This release improves upon the DescribeKeyValueStore API by returning two additional fields, Status of the KeyValueStore and the FailureReason in case of failures during creation of KeyValueStore.
[``botocore``] This release adds the ability to view audit history on a case and introduces a new parameter, performedBy, for CreateCase and UpdateCase API's.

[``botocore``] This release adds support for Transport Layer Security (TLS) and Configurable Timeout to ECS Service Connect. TLS facilitates privacy and data security for inter-service communications, while Configurable Timeout allows customized per-request timeout and idle timeout for Service Connect services.
[``botocore``] Allow customer to set zip default through command line arguments.
[``botocore``] Doc only update for quota increase change

[``botocore``] Introduced support for the InsufficientDBInstanceCapacityFault error in the RDS CreateDBCluster API method. This provides enhanced error handling, ensuring a more robust experience when creating database clusters with insufficient instance capacity.
[``botocore``] Update endpoint-rules client to latest version
